until 15-07-2025 and the program is expected to start at 12-10-2026.
Selection criteria and process
The program accepts applications from graduates of Greek Universities or authorized
Universities abroad with a degree in Medicine, Biology, Genetics, Biochemistry,
Biotechnology, Molecular Biology, Cell Biology, Chemistry, Pharmacy, Agriculture,
Informatics, Mathematics. Statistics, or other related disciplines, as well as from graduates
